013.09</span></p>
<h2 id=3D"Howtoretrieverootlocation-Description">Description</h2>
<p>Knowledge of the root location is important since it can be a starting p=
oint for API queries, or even links to home page, but as eZ Publish can be =
used <a href=3D"/display/EZP/Multisite+using+content_root">for multisite de=
velopment</a>, and as such <strong>root location can vary</strong>.</p>
<p>By default, root location ID is <code>2</code>, but as it can be easily =
be changed by configuration, <strong>the best practice is to retrieve it dy=
namically</strong>.</p>
<h2 id=3D"Howtoretrieverootlocation-RetrievingrootlocationID">Retrieving ro=
ot location ID</h2>
<p>Root location ID can be retrieved easily from <a href=3D"/display/EZP/Co=
nfiguration#Configuration-Configuration-DynamicconfigurationwiththeConfigRe=
solver">ConfigResolver</a>. Parameter name is&nbsp;<code><strong>content.tr=
ee_root.location_id</strong></code>.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;">
<b>In a controller</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size=
:12px;">&lt;?php
namespace Acme\TestBundle\Controller;

use eZ\Bundle\EzPublishCoreBundle\Controller;


class DefaultController extends Controller
{
    public function fooAction()
    {
        // ...
&nbsp;
        $rootLocationId =3D $this-&gt;getConfigResolver()-&gt;getParameter(=
 'content.tree_root.location_id' );
&nbsp;
        // ...
    }
}</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"Howtoretrieverootlocation-Retrievingtherootlocation">Retrieving t=
he root location</h2>
<h3 id=3D"Howtoretrieverootlocation-Fromatemplate">From a template</h3>
<p>Root location is exposed in the <a href=3D"/display/EZP/Twig+Helper">glo=
bal Twig helper</a>.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;">
<b>Making a link to homepage</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: html/xml; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font=
-size:12px;">&lt;a href=3D"{{ path( ezpublish.rootLocation ) }}" title=3D"L=
ink to homepage"&gt;Home page&lt;/a&gt;</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"Howtoretrieverootlocation-Fromacontroller">From a controller</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;">
<b>eZ Publish 5.2+ / 2013.11+</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size=
:12px;">&lt;?php
namespace Acme\TestBundle\Controller;

use eZ\Bundle\EzPublishCoreBundle\Controller;

class DefaultController extends Controller
{
    public function fooAction()
    {
        // ...

        $rootLocation =3D $this-&gt;getRootLocation();

        // ...
    }
}</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;">
<b>Before 5.2 / 2013.11</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size=
:12px;">&lt;?php
namespace Acme\TestBundle\Controller;

use eZ\Bundle\EzPublishCoreBundle\Controller;

class DefaultController extends Controller
{
    public function fooAction()
    {
        // ...

        $rootLocationId =3D $this-&gt;getConfigResolver()-&gt;getParameter(=
 'content.tree_root.location_id' );
        $rootLocation =3D $this-&gt;getRepository()-&gt;getLocationService(=
)-&gt;loadLocation( $rootLocationId );

        // ...
    }
}</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
